.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-HTLC-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-htlc-stats \- aggregate HTLC statistics across all channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-htlc-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
Counts in-flight HTLCs across all channels and reports totals for
offered (outbound), received (inbound), and channels that currently
carry at least one HTLC.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{total_htlcs, offered, received, channels_with_htlcs}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-htlc-list (1),
.BR lightning-channel-htlc-count (1)
